Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.74,0:00:07.66,Episode Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(349,408.591)\fade(255,0,255,0,1220,5700,6900)}The Battle of Guāndù (2)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.54,0:00:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,My childhood friend, I never thought we'd meet like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.70,0:00:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,448.034)}I failed to pick the better lord, \Nas I was under that wicked Yuán Shào.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.41,0:00:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,448.034)}My words ignored and my ideas disregarded, \NI chose to abandon him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.18,0:00:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,448.034)}That's why I've come to an old friend, \Nand I hope I can be of service!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.80,0:00:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,448.034)}How brilliant! How brilliant! With your arrival,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.79,0:01:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,448.034)}the blessing of heaven is now mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.46,0:01:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,448.034)}Zǐyuǎn, what plan did you have for me to defeat Yuan?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.46,0:01:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,448.034)}I had told Yuan Shao to target Xǔdū, your most precious territory,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.66,0:01:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,448.034)}and attack you from both front and rear.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.77,0:01:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If Yuan Shao followed your plan, \NI would have been destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.98,0:01:35.94,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(610,345.886)\fade(255,0,255,0,420,3740,3940)}Cáo Cāo\NStyled: Mèngdé
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.74,0:01:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,How much grain is there left in your camp?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.00,0:01:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We could manage for a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.58,0:01:45.74,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(114,328.693)}Xǔ Yōu\NStyled: Zǐyuǎn
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.90,0:01:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.12,0:01:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm only jesting. We've only got half a year left.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.52,0:02:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ziyuan, why act like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.00,0:02:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back! Sit down, Ziyuan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.77,0:02:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to you in sincerity,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.49,0:02:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,yet you'd deceived me so. You disappoint me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.48,0:02:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's not hide from each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.62,0:02:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The grain in the camp is only enough for three months.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.36,0:02:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ziyuan, why are you laughing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.03,0:02:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Many have said you were devious!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.07,0:02:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you know that war{\i1} is{\i0} devious?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.71,0:02:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell this to no one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.01,0:02:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We've only got one month of grain left.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.75,0:03:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you lie to me! You're already out of grain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.56,0:03:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.76,0:03:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You sent someone towards Xǔdū to urge the grain shipments.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.10,0:03:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The letter fell into my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.69,0:03:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you already know the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.36,0:03:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I humbly ask for your strategy against Yuán!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.71,0:03:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.78,0:03:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Away! No one enters my tent without my orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.55,0:03:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.19,0:04:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Esteemed sire, you fight with a lone army against a vast enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.72,0:04:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.72,0:04:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you ask a plan for a quick victory?\N Is that not a path to suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.96,0:04:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever you want to say, Ziyuan, please say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.03,0:04:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,My one plan, in only three days,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.04,0:04:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,could have Yuan Shao's 700,000 man army fall apart on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.24,0:04:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Would my esteemed lord like to hear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.28,0:04:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.95,0:04:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever you wish to say, I will heed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.03,0:04:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I know well that my esteemed lord excels at war,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.94,0:04:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and that he surely knows what's most critical in defeating an opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.17,0:04:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Sever his supply route?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.97,0:05:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,448.034)}Severing his supply route is like choking his throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.30,0:05:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,448.034)}But to defeat Yuan Shao, \Nmerely cutting him from his supplies,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.22,0:05:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,448.034)}may still not mean striking him in the throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.35,0:05:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,448.034)}Ziyuan, there is no need to beat around the bush.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.76,0:05:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,448.034)}Just say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.75,0:05:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,448.034)}Yuan Shao's provisions for all 700,000 of his army.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.40,0:05:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,448.034)}All of it is stored in Wūcháo, that is his{\i1}'throat'.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.14,0:05:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But if that's the 'throat', then surely\NYuan Shao has placed heavy guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.65,0:05:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,How could we feasibly strike it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.05,0:05:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This is why I say we can beat Yuan Shao in three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.76,0:05:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Although Wūcháo is very important,\N Yuan Shao hardly pays notice to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.80,0:05:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He actually sent Chúnyú Qióng to garrison it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.62,0:05:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That Chunyu Qiong is a careless drunkard,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.16,0:06:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,so isn't that like offering Wūcháo\N to you with open palms, my esteemed sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.11,0:06:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,May I ask, Ziyuan, how should our army seize Wūcháo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.80,0:06:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,448.034)}It won't be hard! Just select your elite cavalry,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.46,0:06:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,448.034)}disguise themselves as Yuan Shao's officer Jiǎng Qí,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.56,0:06:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,448.034)}and head towards Wūcháo to 'protect' it, \Nusing this chance to burn it's supplies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.14,0:06:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,448.034)}Thus in three days, Yuan's army will be in disarray.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.96,0:06:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. I'll head to Wūcháo personally!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.88,0:06:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor, seizing supplies is risky! \NYou should not lead the attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.34,0:06:50.34,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(114,361.057)\fade(255,0,255,0,380,2660,2980)}Xǔ Chǔ\NStyled: Zhòngkāng
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.54,0:06:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If the Chancellor goes personally, there may be disaster! Please reconsider!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.66,0:06:56.90,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(114,361.057)\fade(255,0,255,0,380,2660,2980)}Zhang Liáo\NStyled: Wényuăn
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.74,0:06:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The validity of Xǔ Yōu's plan is still unknown! \NYou should not be so trusting!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.73,0:07:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wūcháo is Yuan Shao's granary. \NHow could he not defend it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.40,0:07:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Xǔ Yōu may be duplicitous. Do not go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.40,0:07:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Moreover, how could 5,000 men beat\N Chunyu Qiong’s tens of thousands?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.57,0:07:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Report!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.58,0:07:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor, 5,000 elite soldiers are ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.31,0:07:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.45,0:07:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,How is this good?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.27,0:07:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,448.034)}Wūcháo is the 'throat' for Yuan Shao.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.03,0:07:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,448.034)}Raiding his supplies is
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.44,0:07:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,448.034)}what determines our final outcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.45,0:07:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,448.034)}Xǔ Yōu's defection is Heaven's will helping me defeat Yuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.20,0:07:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,448.034)}Our supplies are gone, so entrenchment is difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.90,0:07:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,448.034)}If we do not use Xǔ Yōu's plan,\N it is no different than waiting for death.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.09,0:07:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,448.034)}Moreover, raiding the supplies had occupied my mind for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.46,0:07:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,448.034)}Gentlemen, do not doubt it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.42,0:08:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If you go, I fear Yuan Shao will exploit this feint to attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.17,0:08:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I've made my decision!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.68,0:08:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor, please give the order!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.56,0:08:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,When dusk parts, we shall head towards Wūcháo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.96,0:08:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Relay my orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.36,0:08:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Raise a fire on all sides! We shall strike together!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.97,0:08:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.86,0:09:00.62,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(595,363.08)\fade(255,0,255,0,380,1380,1740)}Chúnyú Qióng\NStyled: Zhòngjiān
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.58,0:09:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this commotion?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.94,0:10:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,General, look! Wūcháo is on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.56,0:10:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wūcháo is in danger! Have the rear-troops save the provisions!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.54,0:10:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone else, follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.68,0:10:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.16,0:10:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Reporting! Suī Yuánjìn and Zhào Ruì\N led troops to attack us from behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.78,0:11:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Officeers, keep charging forward with all your strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.90,0:11:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Deal with them when they get behind us! Now onward!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.71,0:11:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor, Yuan's troops are already here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.08,0:11:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Rearguard, turn and fight to the death!\N Force your way through!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.95,0:11:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.41,0:11:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, Wūcháo is in flames!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.38,0:11:46.42,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(108,363.08)}Yuán Shào\NStyled: Běnchū
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.22,0:11:53.66,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(90,336.784)\fade(255,0,255,0,380,2100,2420)}Gāo Lǎn
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.35,0:11:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, Zhāng Hé and I are willing to rescue it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.32,0:11:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, no! If they're seizing the supplies, then Cáo Cāo must be there himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.02,0:12:01.18,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(587,367.125)\fade(255,0,255,0,380,2780,3140)}Guō Tú\NStyled: Gōngzé
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.06,0:12:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,In his absence, his camp must be empty!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.50,0:12:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We should send troops to attack their camp!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.32,0:12:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Upon hearing of this, Cao Cao will rush there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.47,0:12:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,His troops will be exhausted. Thus we can crush him, and inflict a great loss!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.12,0:12:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Sūn Bìn's {\i1}"Besiege Wèi to rescue Zhào"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.12,0:12:14.22,Note (Potential style?),,0,0,0,,Note: Sūn Bìn of the Warring States period suggested sieging Wèi to distract the troops attacking Zhào, thus rescuing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.76,0:12:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Reasonable!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.51,0:12:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Cao Cao is cunning, if he left camp he would've already made preparations.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.65,0:12:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If we attack the camp and fail,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.46,0:12:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,when they return from Wūcháo, \Nwe'll be caught in a pincer attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.82,0:12:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That would only exasperate our situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.22,0:12:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Cao Cao only cares about larceny. \NHow could he spare troops for his camp?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.46,0:12:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! My lord, make your \Nchoice now, and raid their camp!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.08,0:12:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord! Wūcháo is more important!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.83,0:12:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of your plans...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.03,0:12:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you two...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.50,0:12:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.74,0:12:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Your words are...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.16,0:12:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They're both correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.35,0:12:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Zhang He and Gāo Lǎn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.90,0:12:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.58,0:12:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Lead 5,000 men towards \NGuāndù and raid their camp!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.49,0:12:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.62,0:13:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Order Jiang Qi to take 10,000 men towards Wūcháo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.92,0:13:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,General,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.41,0:13:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,were you sober last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.80,0:13:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If you are indeed sober, raise your eyes and see
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.47,0:13:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,that {\i1}this{\i0} is your dear, heavily guarded Wūcháo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.55,0:13:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just as Ziyuan said:
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.95,0:14:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,How could Wūcháo not be lost \Nwhen Yuan Shao sent you to defend it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.85,0:14:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Men?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.70,0:14:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.69,0:14:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Tattoo Chunyu Qiong's face and body.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.79,0:14:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Let him go back to Yuan Shao to humiliate him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.11,0:14:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.27,0:14:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Have all regiments disguise as Chunyu Qiong's \Ndefeated soldiers and rush back to Guāndù!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.48,0:14:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If any come to save Wūcháo, kill them along the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.08,0:14:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.50,0:14:53.86,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(128,378.25)\fade(255,0,255,0,380,2020,2340)}Xiàhóu Yuān\NStyled: Miàocái
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.12,0:15:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,General, if we go any further, I fear \Nwe'll be recognized by the Yuan troops!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.49,0:15:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Which group are you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.34,0:15:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We're Chunyu Qiong's subordinates!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.40,0:15:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We were defeated by Cao Cao's forces!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.74,0:15:31.10,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(224,259.92)\fade(255,0,255,0,350,1940,2340)}Jiǎng Qí
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.14,0:15:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Onward to Wūcháo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.68,0:15:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiang Qi, halt!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.35,0:15:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We surrender! We surrender!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.40,0:16:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Send men to disguise as Jiang Qi's \Nsubordinates to Yuan Shao's main camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.44,0:16:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Just say Jiang Qi has already defeated our forces and recovered Wūcháo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.25,0:16:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.80,0:16:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry back to Guāndù!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.12,0:16:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Lift your head for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.28,0:16:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.31,0:16:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that on your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.80,0:16:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Words...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.42,0:16:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What words?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.32,0:16:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.72,0:16:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.43,0:17:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It is... {\i1}the Drunkard of Wūcháo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.81,0:17:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You drunk? You drunk!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.68,0:17:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let you drink your fill!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.81,0:17:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Men!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.38,0:17:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.91,0:17:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Take him away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.24,0:17:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Drown him in wine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.35,0:17:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.47,0:17:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Let him drink his fill!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.98,0:17:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord! My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.24,0:17:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Report!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.43,0:17:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.99,0:17:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, General Jiang Qi sent a messenger!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.56,0:17:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He's already defeated the Cao troops at Wūcháo, and recaptured it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.23,0:17:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... then... then what about Guāndù?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.22,0:17:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Zhang He and Gao Lan are currently engaged in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.57,0:17:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The results are unclear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.74,0:17:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... then send more troops to Guāndù!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.65,0:17:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You must take Guāndù!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.25,0:17:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.62,0:17:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,How is the battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.52,0:18:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just as Zhang He said.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.47,0:18:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Zhang He and Gao Lan's persistent attack failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.89,0:18:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Cao Cao got them from behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.03,0:18:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are Zhang He and Gao Lan now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.57,0:18:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,According to defeated troops, they broke out with a hundred or so cavalry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.40,0:18:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Their current location is unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.71,0:18:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If they return,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.84,0:18:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,how could our lord not want to blame you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.95,0:18:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Did those two survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.13,0:18:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.45,0:18:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,How fares Guāndù?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.51,0:19:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not going well!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.02,0:19:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not going well?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.82,0:19:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if it is like that, does Cao Cao have an elite force at Guāndù?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.86,0:19:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.66,0:19:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, are you still unaware of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.17,0:19:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Guāndù had small defenses,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.11,0:19:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,but Zhang He and Gao Lan had no will to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.51,0:19:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.28,0:19:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Those two have long wanted to surrender!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.92,0:19:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They intentionally refused to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.69,0:19:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,They dare to mock me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.63,0:19:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Emergency! Emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.20,0:19:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.82,0:19:53.22,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(94,250.818)}Zhāng Hé
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.53,0:19:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Guō Tú sent me to report this to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.76,0:19:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The lord is furious!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.10,0:19:59.86,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(525,302.398)}Gāo Lǎn
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.18,0:20:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He said you two didn't even try to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.20,0:20:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.21,0:20:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants you executed as an example to the entire army!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.45,0:20:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Who said we didn't fight!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.85,0:20:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an emergency, so I wouldn't dare remain here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.87,0:20:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.23,0:20:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be careful my generals.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.50,0:20:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We fought with all we had,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.24,0:20:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,yet this is what we get for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.34,0:20:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Our Lordship's messenger has arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.58,0:20:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Salutations to two generals.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.75,0:20:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Generals, our lord has asked you two to return to camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.26,0:20:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Why has our lord summoned us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.56,0:20:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.73,0:20:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I truly don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.70,0:20:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.17,0:20:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,General don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.58,0:21:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuan Shao listens only to slander and lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.15,0:21:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He will be defeated sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.80,0:21:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How could we sit and wait for death?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.90,0:21:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Better to surrender to Cao Cao!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.83,0:21:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,By the Chancellor's orders,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.54,0:21:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Zhang He and Gao Lan may enter the camp!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.60,0:22:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.60,0:22:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The surrendering general is the one at Guāndù who
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.16,0:22:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,matched against Zhāng Liáo in a fifty-bout duel, Zhang He!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.15,0:22:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall go out to meet them personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.41,0:22:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.95,0:22:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Zhang He and Gao Lan coming to defect so suddenly is suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.09,0:22:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Should you really meet them?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.70,0:22:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall treat them graciously.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.66,0:22:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If they possess ulterior motives, I will change their heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.13,0:23:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.30,0:23:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Generals, since you've come from afar to join me,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.96,0:23:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,you have gained my respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.93,0:23:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.34,0:23:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Please rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.51,0:23:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You generals joining me is like Weizi leaving Yīn(-Shāng) and Hán Xìn joining Hàn.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.51,0:24:02.80,Note (Potential style?),,0,0,0,,Note: Weizi was a duke known for his virtue who joined the Zhou to defeat \Nthe Shang dynasty, and Han Xin was instrumental in the rise of the Han dynasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.38,0:24:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Now now, please rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.10,0:24:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Please rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.66,0:24:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Beat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.50,0:24:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone else who spreads rumors and disturbs morale,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.80,0:24:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,beat them!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.38,0:24:36.18,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(129,374.205)\fade(255,0,255,0,400,2420,2780)}Yuán Tán\NStyled: Xiǎnsī
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.52,0:24:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Beat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.52,0:24:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Beat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.08,0:25:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.65,0:25:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.25,0:25:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.82,0:25:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here instead \Nof staying in your camp?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.89,0:25:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Father,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.24,0:25:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,a few defeats won't decide our fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.96,0:25:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, I know you're upset, but you shoudn't drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.42,0:26:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Xǔ Yōu left.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.69,0:26:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Zhang He and Gao Lan have betrayed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.99,0:26:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, the people are aggrieved!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.85,0:26:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.07,0:26:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord! He died! He died!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.11,0:26:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.15,0:26:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You scum!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.58,0:26:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Men!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.64,0:26:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.90,0:26:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Have this ill-tongued bastard taken away!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.72,0:26:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And flog him 300 times!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.65,0:26:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.54,0:27:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord! My lord! Spare–
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.44,0:27:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Afterwards, ask him who died!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.06,0:27:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.31,0:27:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Scum! I want him beaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.35,0:27:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Spare me!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.00,0:27:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.55,0:27:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Beat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.82,0:27:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.35,0:27:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Beat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.61,0:27:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Beat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.55,0:27:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Beat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.46,0:27:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We are falling apart, not due to \Nthe enemy, but due to ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.40,0:27:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.48,0:27:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, you should rest now for your own good.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.35,0:28:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, I've discovered someone else \Nwho seeks to disturb our military's morale.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.89,0:28:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,An officer in the rear camp said to someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.93,0:28:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,"At the rate things are going, it won't take long
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.44,0:28:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,for us to be defeated by Cao Cao."
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.65,0:28:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.28,0:28:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Every word and sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.25,0:28:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Seize that man! Execute him!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.82,0:28:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Let his body be shown to the entire army! Anyone else who disturbs morale,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.20,0:28:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,anyone else who spreads rumors, I'll kill them myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.80,0:28:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.11,0:28:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.78,0:28:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.31,0:29:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You must ensure our units are on guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.44,0:29:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is most important to our military's morale.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.69,0:29:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.62,0:29:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.01,0:31:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Generals!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.08,0:31:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonight, we defeat the Yuan's forces!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.95,0:31:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Surround them from all sides!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.08,0:31:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Annihilate them!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.51,0:32:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister Tián Fēng!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.62,0:32:26.78,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(129,374.205)\fade(255,0,255,0,400,1820,2140)}Tián Fēng\NStyled: Yuánhào
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.69,0:32:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.85,0:32:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister Tian, my utmost felicitations for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.13,0:32:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you congratulating me?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.70,0:32:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,General Yuan is returning from Guandu in great defeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.51,0:32:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,700,000 troops were all annihilated!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.42,0:33:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,In the beginning, you urged our lordship \Nnot to raise a too large an army too early.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.26,0:33:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you've been proven right! Our lordship is returning!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.42,0:33:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't this mean getting back your position?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.60,0:33:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister Tian, what is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.12,0:33:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I will die soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.60,0:33:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister Tian Feng!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.70,0:33:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.45,0:33:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,448.034)}General Yuan seems open but is petty,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.52,0:33:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,448.034)}he does not heed loyalty and honesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.07,0:33:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,448.034)}If he had won, in his bliss I would be pardoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.14,0:34:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,448.034)}Yet he had lost, he will meet with me in shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.98,0:34:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,448.034)}There is no hope for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.63,0:34:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister Tian Feng, that...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.46,0:34:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.20,0:34:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.37,0:34:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,By our lord's orders, we shall take Tian Feng's head!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.44,0:34:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister Tian Feng!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.60,0:34:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor, Yuan Shao escaped \Nwith only 800 of his remaining cavalry!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.00,0:35:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Heaven's will! They are doomed to have an arduous escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.85,0:35:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Jǔ Shòu?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.94,0:35:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Ju Shou!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.78,0:35:24.66,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(579,333.75)\fade(255,0,255,0,380,1500,1860)}Jǔ Shòu
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.05,0:35:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Ju Shou.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.91,0:35:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry. Release this gentleman.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.64,0:35:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.60,0:35:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I will never surrender!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.10,0:36:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuan Benchu had no wit and never used thy words.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.31,0:36:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Why the fervor for the ignorant?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.15,0:36:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Had I received you, nothing on this realm could worry me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.10,0:36:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, you have great ability, \Nbut could not find a wise lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.63,0:36:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I value your knowledge and talent, \N I would like to achieve greatness with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.67,0:36:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I would enjoy your tutelage.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.70,0:37:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Build a tomb for Master Ju \Non the banks of the Yellow River.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.95,0:37:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.10,0:37:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you so rattled about?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.80,0:37:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,448.034)}Chancellor, people within Xǔdū messaged with Yuan Shao in secrecy.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.98,0:37:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,448.034)}The letters were written in most sycophantic words.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.46,0:37:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.68,0:37:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,448.034)}Chancellor,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.46,0:37:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,448.034)}Chancellor can mark down every name on these letters, then arrest and execute each.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.12,0:38:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,448.034)}Have them torched.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.12,0:38:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,448.034)}Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.50,0:38:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.20,0:38:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.68,0:38:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,448.034)}When Yuán Shào had the upper-hand, I could barely even save myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.90,0:38:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,448.034)}... Let alone them?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.80,0:38:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.14,0:38:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,These elders have come to offer wine to the Chancellor!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.76,0:38:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.36,0:39:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,448.034)}Chancellor, during the reign of Emperor Huán,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.36,0:39:01.70,Note (Potential style?),,0,0,0,,Emperor Huán of Hàn, 132 – 168 AD.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.70,0:39:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,448.034)}there were people that predicted that after 50 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.54,0:39:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,448.034)}a certain benevolent man would climb here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.40,0:39:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,448.034)}From today, 50 years have passed!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.58,0:39:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,448.034)}Yuan Shao has burdened his people, and thus they all dislike him.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.98,0:39:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,448.034)}Chancellor, you raised a most righteous campaign
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.66,0:39:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,448.034)}to relieve their suffering. And in the battle of Guāndù,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.38,0:39:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,448.034)}you defeated the hundred-thousand hordes of the Yuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.69,0:39:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,448.034)}This is what was said 50 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.34,0:39:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,448.034)}It's a sign that the people may now look forward to peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.95,0:39:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.26,0:39:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't possibly receive this boon!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.96,0:39:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor, we were born of this yellow earth \Nand drank from the yellow river for nearly a century.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.23,0:39:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I deceive before this great river?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.21,0:39:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.86,0:40:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.42,0:40:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If so, forgive your junior for acting on his own,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.36,0:40:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,but I shall offer to this earth the wine and this water
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.90,0:40:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,to nurture such kindness as yours for ten thousand years.
